# Helper Functions Reference

## SVG Icons

```php
/**
 * Generates an SVG icon using sprite.
 *
 * @param string $icon       Icon name (without 'icon-' prefix).
 * @param array  $attributes Optional. Additional attributes.
 *                           - 'class': Additional CSS classes
 *                           - 'aria-hidden': 'true' for decorative icons
 *                           - 'width', 'height': Dimensions
 * @return string SVG HTML markup.
 *
 * @example
 * echo skel_get_svg_svg( 'arrow-right' );
 * echo skel_get_svg_svg( 'arrow-right', [ 'class' => 'icon-lg', 'aria-hidden' => 'true' ] );
 */
function skel_get_svg_svg( $icon, $attributes = array() ) {}
```

