## Excerpts

```php
/**
 * Retrieves a truncated excerpt for a post.
 *
 * @param int      $limit   Word limit. Default 50.
 * @param int|null $post_id Post ID. Default current post.
 * @return string Truncated excerpt with '...' if exceeded.
 *
 * @example
 * echo esc_html( skel_get_the_excerpt( 20 ) );
 * echo esc_html( skel_get_the_excerpt( 30, $post_id ) );
 */
function skel_get_the_excerpt( int $limit = 50, ?int $post_id = null ): string {}

/**
 * Shorten text to specified length, preserving whole words.
 *
 * @param string $input  The input text.
 * @param int    $length Maximum character length.
 * @return string Shortened text with '...' appended.
 *
 * @example
 * echo esc_html( skel_get_text_shorter( $title, 100 ) );
 */
function skel_get_text_shorter( string $input, int $length ): string {}
```

